'''數位看板'''是一種以[[電腦|電腦]]控制[[數位影像|數位影像]]動態顯示內容的[[看板|看板]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oaaa.org/outofhomeadvertising/oohmediaformats/digitalbillboards.aspx|title=Outdoor Advertising Association of America, Inc. > About OOH > OOH Basics > OOH Media Formats > Digital Billboards|first=Outdoor Advertising Association of America|last=Inc.|website=www.oaaa.org|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222174153/http://www.oaaa.org/outofhomeadvertising/oohmediaformats/digitalbillboards.aspx|archivedate=2014-02-22}}</ref>。

== 安全隱患 ==
數位看板所帶來的[[交通安全|交通安全]]問題一直受人關注。{{link-en|聯邦公路局|Federal Highway Administration}}在2001年進行研究以檢視數位看板對車禍率的影響。根據其研究，當時似乎未有有效的技術或方法來評估數位看板對駕駛者的注意力的安全性影響<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fhwa.dot.gov/realestate/elecbbrd/chap3.htm|title=Electronic Billboards - Outdoor Advertising Control - Real Estate - FHWA|website=www.fhwa.dot.gov|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623235333/http://www.fhwa.dot.gov/realestate/elecbbrd/chap3.htm|archivedate=2010-06-23}}</ref>。此後更廣泛的研究則證實數位看板對駕駛者的注意力的負面影響<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rightofway.transportation.org/Documents/NCHRP%20Reports/20-7(256)%20digital%20outdoor%20advertising_aashto.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321214818/http://rightofway.transportation.org/Documents/NCHRP%20Reports/20-7%28256%29%20digital%20outdoor%20advertising_aashto.pdf|archivedate=2014-03-21|title=Safety Impacts of the Emerging Digital Display Technology for Outdoor Advertising Signs|last=Wachtel|first=Jerry|date=2009-04-22|website=Transportation Research Board of the National Academies|publisher=National Cooperative Highway Research Program|accessdate=2014-03-21|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/LandArch/research/docs/Digital_Display_Safety_Preliminary_Investigation_10-11-12_final.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321215347/http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/LandArch/research/docs/Digital_Display_Safety_Preliminary_Investigation_10-11-12_final.pdf|archivedate=2014-03-21|title=Effects of Outdoor Advertising Displays on Driver Safety|date=2012-10-11|website=California Department of Transportation|publisher=Caltrans Division of Research and Innovation|accessdate=2014-03-21}}</ref>。

